- "blossoming flowers" refers to the titles of songs;
- "opened their petals" symbolizes becoming popular;
- "since the dawn of spring 2013" refers to the release date being after May 1, 2013;
- "garden visitors" are listeners;
- "admirers" indicate the number of plays;
- "what kind of garden" refers to the genre in which the song is categorized.

